    "However, unlike BLIP-2, LLaVA focuses on training data and procedure as opposed to the model architecture.",
    "It is the first model that extends instruction-tuning to the language-image multimodal space.",
    "LLaVA achieves this by collecting and training on visionlanguage instruction-following data, constructed for <image, caption> pairs of existing datasets (e.g., COCO), by querying GPT-4 (OpenAI, 2023) using various in-context-learning prompts.",
